Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:23.69,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The flowers dance to a piano's rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:25.49,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Two people face-to-face are a mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:27.47,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The doc and I are in big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.47,0:00:29.67,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The Detective Boys and a treasure that vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:31.56,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:33.55,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:35.98,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.24,0:00:19.99,Signs,,0,0,0,,Treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:22.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We, the Detective Boys, went camping with Dr. Agasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.65,0:02:25.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the way back, we got lost on the mountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.84,0:02:28.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and ended up finding a castle in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.56,0:02:32.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, they allowed us to stay for the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.62,0:02:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the owners of the castle, the Mamiya family,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:36.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,seemed to have some ulterior motive...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inside the castle, I found a secret passageway,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and a skeleton in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:15.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.67,0:03:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello? Is this the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.13,0:03:30.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm calling on behalf of Shin'ichi Kud≈ç.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you pass me to Inspector Megure, from the 1st division of the investigation department?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calling a friend, little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:40.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello, Megure here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:42.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.69,0:03:46.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is where you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, where'd you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:54.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our beds are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:55.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Where's the doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:57.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't he with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:03:58.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:04:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's trying to find this castle's treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:19.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The doctor's bed's still empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:21.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Something must have happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:31.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Either way, I have to investigate what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:42.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:51.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because we're worried about Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The doc hasn't come back, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we thought we'd help with the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:59.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a lot easier for four people than for just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:00.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you get murdered, I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:08.57,Signs,,0,0,0,,- Hey!\N- What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:16.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:18.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The room we were in during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, can you please put that chair under the clock on that wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:35.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What on earth are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:47.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A secret passageway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manually moving the clock's hands triggers a mechanism that opens the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:56.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:03.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A flashlight-watch that Dr. Agasa gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:06.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He gave you one too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:07.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"You too?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:12.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:21.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a long staircase...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:29.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:31.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:36.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By its color and dryness, it hasn't been here for many hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.94,0:06:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing! Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you look just like Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:42.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you so happy about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:45.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This could be his blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:51.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something written in the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:59.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"That person trapped me here and is trying to steal the castle's treas..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:02.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds like he meant to write 'treasure...'
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:05.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} have written this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.39,0:07:08.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, from the style, it doesn't sound like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the writing looks old.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.52,0:07:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then who wrote this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:14.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know who wrote it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since the person didn't finish writing 'treasure,'
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:21.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he or she probably was unable to finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:24.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unable?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.93,0:07:26.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:29.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. He or she could have died here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:35.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} must have found the body, and taking advantage of his distraction,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:40.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,somebody must have attacked him or stabbed him from the back. That would explain the blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:42.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Something fell down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:47.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They look like glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! Aren't those the doctor's glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:55.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are the doc's glasses doing here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:57.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're broken and bloody...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.73,0:07:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something must have happened to the doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:04.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:05.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:14.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is where I lost sight of the doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.92,0:08:17.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.32,0:08:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time I can't seem to open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s still in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:23.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:27.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll have to go back to the starting point and find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:32.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn! What's going on? It just opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:42.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems to have been locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:45.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why? It was open before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody must have followed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:54.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They locked the door to prevent us from leaving the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:58.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we happened to be able to get out with that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:09:00.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what about Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:06.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must have fallen into the hands of the one following us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:08.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.89,0:09:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either way, let's go find another way onto that passageway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:17.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While there's a chance our three missing friends may still be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:21.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a big room...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:24.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems to be what Takahito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} uses as a workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:26.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They did mention he was a painter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:33.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a lot of newspapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.06,0:09:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're used to cover the paintings, or to dry the brushes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either way, these newspapers are very old.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:42.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:45.06,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Big fire at Mamiya residence"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:45.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...the fire from four years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:59.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:07.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Fifteen people died in the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:10.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The fire burned the bodies into ash, down to the bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:13.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Their identities were estimated from the objects they carried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:16.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}One person is still missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:20.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Using that fire, a person could pass off as another...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:23.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:31.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he went through that door...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:32.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:37.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's the door leading to the burned tower, which was supposed to be locked...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:40.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko-{\i1}k{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:42.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:43.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could be a trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go inside and take a look,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.69,0:10:50.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,while you go hide in the bushes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Count up to 300, and if I'm not out by then, run away immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:11:01.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you take the road through the forest, you can still save yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:02.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:03.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Put yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You brought that bread for Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:27.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,2... 3... 4... 5...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:33.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,83... 84... 85... 86...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:37.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,153... 154... 155...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:40.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,298... 299...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,3... 300.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:56.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,300... I counted them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:07.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:16.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.87,0:12:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:27.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Count up to 300, and if I'm not out by then, run away immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.75,0:12:32.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If you take the road through the forest, you can still save yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.51,0:12:34.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:36.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:37.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can't run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:40.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Because I have to give Conan{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10} this bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:45.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not... scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.77,0:12:51.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:52.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.61,0:13:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:16.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...is the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:24.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:26.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's {\i1}not{\i0} Haibara{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:06.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.89,0:14:11.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here? Didn't I tell you to run?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:15.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were saved because I just {\i1}happened{\i0} to be in the secret door, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...if I hadn't been there, you'd have been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:22.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With everybody else in danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:25.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't just escape by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:29.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:30.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, wash your tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And let's go find everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:39.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey... Where's Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:45.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was in this tower, then that person from now probably caught him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and the others are gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:02.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, what happened with your Detective Boys badges?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:06.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were out of batteries, so we gave them to the doc...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:13.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look! There's somebody here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:16.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:21.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:30.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the bones like this, it's been years since this person died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:35.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But considering the dust, the skeleton was placed here recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:39.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This might be the person who wrote in that staircase.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:44.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe the skeleton was moved here after Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:48.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:52.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Compared to the other bones, the leg bones are extremely thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:56.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Furthermore, the teeth are worn out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:58.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And this hairstyle seems to be that of a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:02.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No way! Then the killer who's pretending to be her is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.55,0:16:06.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:10.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard voices and came to see what was going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Where are your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bad person kidnapped all of my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:22.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:28.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! If we don't take the old lady with us, she might be attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:32.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? She's the one who attacked you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:36.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The leg bones in that skeleton were those of a person who hadn't walked in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:40.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Combined with its sex and age, it has to be the body of the family's grandmother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:42.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.24,0:16:44.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She killed the grandmother to impersonate her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:49.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She got plastic surgery and pretended to have a bad memory to fool everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:51.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It happened on the day of that fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:56.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the real woman's daughter wouldn't believe her deception she burnt her to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.19,0:17:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She knew about these secret passageways, and used them to start the fire unnoticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:05.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, she got plastic surgery to change her face and returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And her objective was this castle's treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:15.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:18.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The grandmother figured out I'd came to the castle for the treasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I got rid of her and took her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:24.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our voices were similar, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:27.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.39,0:17:32.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't lock you in that dark basement like I did the grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:39.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll be unconscious, and after 2 to 3 days, I'll drop you off in the forest with your friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.48,0:17:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll have pale cheeks and look like Smart{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. {smart-san is some jp pop culture thing, go figure}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:50.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:55.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Putting kids on a forced diet is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:59.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. They're both fine the way they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:02.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right. Having a full belly is much healthier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G... Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:07.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:09.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was thanks to Mitsuhiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:12.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With my glasses' tracking function,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.39,0:18:18.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he followed the transmitters in our Detective Badges that the doc had, and found us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:20.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.21,0:18:22.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait. There's no use running.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:26.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the missing housekeeper, Mutsumi Nishikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I asked about you to a plastic surgeon who knew your true identity, he knew it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:40.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Have you heard of a weird patient who got surgery to look like an old lady?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:44.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you saw the corpse too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:48.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if we hadn't, we'd still know you're a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:54.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you really were a grandmother who spent the last ten years locked in this castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.84,0:18:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you couldn't have talked about how inconvenient
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:19:00.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it was for the passport sizes to change six years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:06.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unless, of course, you had to frequently travel abroad to keep that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Congratulations. But I know these secret passageways so you'll never be able to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:19.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though I know where the secret passageway is that you want so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Don't tell me you managed to figure out the mystery of the chess pieces?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:29.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.58,0:19:32.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A chess piece's position is often determined by an alphabet letter, from A to H,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:35.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and a number, from 1 to 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the Knight's face, we can see that the stone path is the right place to watch the chess board.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:44.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looking from that position, putting letters to the white pieces, you get...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, an intellectual person who argues a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:57.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. This code points to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:59.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...the castle's former owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:05.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, if you turn the painting to the right as the black pieces show...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.01,0:20:15.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The secret passageway opens to a smiling face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:20.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Twenty years serving in this castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The treasure I searched for is finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:26.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't let anyone have it, it's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:33.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the other side of that shining door...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:35.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...is my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:48.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.25,0:20:50.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:51.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:53.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It says so on the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:21:01.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I offer this wonderful view of the castle to the first person to arrive here."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:09.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I killed dozens of people for something like {\i1}this{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.65,0:21:15.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I changed my face to an ugly old lady's for something like {\i1}this{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:20.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For something like this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:26.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}An hour later, the police came and took away the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:36.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Having lost her soul, she was a pathetic figure who truly became an old lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:02.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Mitsuru{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} was disappointed with the castle's treasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.76,0:23:07.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but the son, Takahito{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}, was happy that the killer had been caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.27,0:23:10.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Apparently, he had suspicions about the fire from four years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:14.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and had been secretly investigating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.48,0:23:17.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Those secret passageways were part of the castle's original construction,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:23.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and the former owner, a historian, made sure to rebuild them correctly during the restoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.70,0:23:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This castle was pretty interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.41,0:23:27.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lots of thrill and suspense!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.37,0:23:28.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.87,0:23:32.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey. Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and I were attacked...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.83,0:23:34.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.29,0:23:38.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master Takahito says breakfast is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.09,0:23:42.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come and eat. The boy in glasses didn't eat anything at all last night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.72,0:23:44.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.18,0:23:47.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have food for camping on the car,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.56,0:23:50.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I've got this bread, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.02,0:23:51.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like it's really tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.23,0:23:57.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, since you're inviting, I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.64,0:23:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.02,0:24:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.76,0:00:03.48,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"Treasure."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:06.43,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Though there are some which bring happiness to people,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.43,0:00:09.07,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}there are also those whose glow deludes people's hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.07,0:00:11.92,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and leads them to commit crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:15.89,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today, the secrets of the treasure hiding in the castle are unveiled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:19.99,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}as we play back "The Old Blue Castle Exploration Case (Part II)!"
